collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description: The little gnome is yelling "wen coin"! Well a treasure trove of these 1024 coins were found in a Bronze suburb commons. They will be distributed evenly amongst Bronze residents and the discoverer, with a Jan 1 2022 snapshot. What happens with them next is up to you.

collectible.name: Basic Gnome Hat of the Air Faction
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description: It's raining hats! If you've received this Scarcity airdrop, it means the discovery you presented was linked to a certain gnome faction determined by its color or properties. You can team up with others in your faction to create new lore, improved hats, other faction items, themed art shows, contests, or other events! Extra hats will be available for purchase if you'd like to switch factions or invite a friend to the story who doesn't own land. All proceeds will go to planting real life trees.

collectible.name: Common Diamond Cut - Pink
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f
collectible.description:
Welcome to the Air faction, Pink!

I know what you're thinking.. how can a diamond be "common"? Well, the gnomes who lived here were excellent gem cutters, and just because this stone was cut in the shape of a diamond.. doesn't make it an actual diamond. Or is it? You can create your own rare art derivatives. Team up and use what the gnomes gave to turn pennies into riches.

After copies are distributed to an active 1st and/or 2nd owner, the remaining quantity of this NFT *might* be burned.

collectible.name: Green Apple
collectible.author: 0xae369b72d56b843719628c7c622d925843b5bf25
collectible.description:
Amazing Devya's Green Apple character is now a wearable. You can now be a green apple or have it as a pet friend by your side in cryptovoxels.

                                                                              
 Devya has a unique way of drawing her characters with emotions. Devya created the green apple on paper in June 2021. Devya's mom made the voxel green apple as commemorative wearable for Amazing Devya's first ever winter wonderland Christmas party 2021. It was a part of holiday build contest and it won a honorary mention, thanks to the green apple. Green apple is a happy apple that spreads smiles everywhere it goes.
